data.description: Welcome to your next home located in the Shenandoah Subdivision in Elgin! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the living area, which is open to the dining area, perfect for entertaining guests and spending time with family. The space has an abundance of natural light flooding through the windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that you'll love. The kitchen is a home chef's dream, with sleek black appliances, a convenient center island, and just the right amount of cabinet space to store all your kitchen essentials. French doors will lead you to the covered deck, perfect for your next summer BBQ. The primary suite features a cozy bedroom, a vanity with makeup table, large walk-in closet & a separate garden tub. Just imagine yourself sinking into the tub with a good book or your favorite podcast playing in the background – pure bliss! This home is designed to make your life easier and more organized. With ample built-in shelving located in the utility room and large closets, you'll have plenty of storage space for all your belongings. Plus, the location couldn't be more perfect! You'll be right in the heart of everything, with nearby restaurants, shopping, schools, Downtown Elgin & Elgin Memorial Park. And with easy access to highways and major roads, your daily commute will be a breeze. Schedule your showing today!     New AC and New Roof
